1. *Oči* su najvažniji organ za vid. (Eyes are the most important organ for sight.)
2. Ona je imala lepe *oči*. (She had beautiful eyes.)
3. Pogledao je u njene tamne *oči*. (He looked into her dark eyes.)
4. Dete je bilo zapanjeno onim čime su ga njegove *oči* gledale. (The child was amazed by what his eyes were seeing.)
5. On je imao ogromne *oči*. (He had huge eyes.)
6. Ona se smešila i njene *oči* su sjale. (She smiled and her eyes were shining.)
7. Njegove *oči* su se ispunile suzama. (His eyes filled with tears.)
8. Ona je držala *oči* otvorene. (She kept her eyes open.)